query: SELECT supervisor_district, analysis_neighborhood, date_trunc_ym(data_loaded_at) AS month, COUNT(*) AS count WHERE data_loaded_at >= '2022-09-01' GROUP BY supervisor_district, analysis_neighborhood, month ORDER BY month, supervisor_district, analysis_neighborhood

analysis_neighborhood.description: The neighborhood used for analysis purposes.

data_loaded_at.description: The date when the data was loaded.

table_metadata.title: San Francisco Mid-Block Points
table_metadata.description: This dataset contains points representing the midpoint of each block in the City of San Francisco used for geomasking and other anonymization tasks.
